⭐ 9. Memory Map Summary

	This subsystem uses a tight, deterministic memory layout:

	d06010–d0601F → pixel masks

	d06020–d0602E → Bresenham engine

	d06035–d0603B → coordinates

	d0603D → pixel attribute

	d063A2 → mode selector
